---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Service Providers', url: '/for-providers' },
  { name: 'Transport', url: '/for-providers/transport' }
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Animal Transport Services on BreederHQ Marketplace"
  description="List your animal transport service on the BreederHQ Marketplace: ground, air, and semen shipping. Get found by breeders and owners. Free to list."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
<main>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-emerald-50 to-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🚐</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">Transport Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Ground transporters, flight nannies, and semen shipping providers -
        breeders, buyers, and pet owners in your area are searching for animal transport on the BreederHQ Marketplace.
      </p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-600">
        List Your Services
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What people search for</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">From Breeders</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Delivery of new animals to buyers (puppies, kittens, foals, kids, lambs, kits)</li>
            <li>Stud transport to and from breeding appointments</li>
            <li>Chilled and frozen semen shipping</li>
            <li>Show circuit transport for competition animals</li>
            <li>USDA-compliant interstate transport</li>
            <li>Climate-controlled vehicle transport</li>
            <li>Flight nanny services for out-of-state buyers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">From Buyers &amp; Pet Owners</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Pickup and delivery of purchased animals</li>
            <li>Long-distance pet relocation</li>
            <li>Airport pickup and flight nanny services</li>
            <li>Safe transport for anxious or special-needs animals</li>
            <li>Cross-country ground transport with updates</li>
            <li>Health certificate coordination for travel</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why it works for transport providers</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔄</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Steady demand</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Every animal sale needs delivery. Breeders ship to buyers year-round, and the same breeder will use a trusted transporter for every litter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📍</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Route-based search</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">People search by origin and destination. Whether it's a local pickup or a cross-country delivery, they find transporters who cover their route.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⭐</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Identity and credentials</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Confirm your identity through Stripe Identity. List the USDA license and insurance you actually hold; both display as your own attestation. BreederHQ does not verify USDA licensure or insurance status.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your listing includes</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Service profile with transport types, routes, and vehicle details</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Coverage area and route-based discovery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Photos of your vehicles and setup</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Flexible pricing display</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Identity confirmation via Stripe Identity. USDA license number is your attestation; BreederHQ does not validate it.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Breeder recommendations from your clients</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900 to-emerald-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Free</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-emerald-200 mb-3">No commissions. Cancel anytime.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-emerald-200 mb-8">One listing puts your services in front of everyone searching for animal transport on the marketplace.</p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-white text-emerald-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-50">
        List Your Services
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
